{"tid":1514380,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟有一樣野想求香港人","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:51:59.000Z","uid":103960,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f0462f43a3408bedece416e4f2c1f0c2dccd87eb","tid":1514380,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"今日聽到好多令人痛心疾首嘅事<br />\n好多手足比人抓左入去大肆凌辱<br />\n或者呢一刻我地救唔到佢地<br />\n<br />\n但我想求求大家<br />\n下次見到有人係你附近比人抓 <br />\n唔好四散逃走<br />\n諗下佢即將面對嘅惡耗<br />\n大聲叫「救人呀」<br />\n然一齊幫手救返手足<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得你地發夢入立法會話過：「要走一齊走」<br />\n<br />\n我真係只係想大家平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a03799b38585157ae355b5fed9999ce477557e","tid":1514380,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69aa6a8f1de1a1264e0edb5d672670eeaf19aa21","tid":1514380,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6599413c14bf9edd16c6256c0e7c83df4e6d2592","tid":1514380,"uid":271956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be56fd25bf6d05179108e3b41bd2e0ea21e4bb3b","tid":1514380,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8963219921f094e5c96371fc56a9cf31fc8fea8d","tid":1514380,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ab43c36c7ebb62b8e540133c106055bf367